37
00:15:03.092 --> 00:15:05.527
My name is Alison.
I was kidnapped just like you.

38
00:15:05.827 --> 00:15:07.762
The guy's not far.
and he's dangerous.

39
00:15:07.796 --> 00:15:09.065
You need to stay quiet.

40
00:15:09.931 --> 00:15:12.701
If he hears us. he's gonna
come back down again.

41
00:15:12.734 --> 00:15:13.768
Okay?

42
00:15:14.736 --> 00:15:16.838
[whimpering]

43
00:15:19.208 --> 00:15:20.508
- Where are we?

44
00:15:25.247 --> 00:15:28.616
- Inside a basement.
but I don't know where.

45
00:15:31.153 --> 00:15:33.155
He grabbed me when I
was coming out of work.

46
00:15:33.189 --> 00:15:34.489
That's all I know. you?

47
00:15:35.057 --> 00:15:36.558
He grabbed me in Asbury Park.

48
00:15:38.626 --> 00:15:39.961
when I was going to my car.

49
00:15:44.333 --> 00:15:46.001
That's far from where I work.

50
00:15:47.569 --> 00:15:50.605
Wouldn't surprise me
if he dragged us
outside the city limits.

51
00:15:53.309 --> 00:15:55.244
- Why is this happening?

52
00:15:55.277 --> 00:15:57.712
[sobbing]

53
00:16:00.349 --> 00:16:02.017
- The guy thinks we're dead.

54
00:16:02.050 --> 00:16:03.551
