55
00:16:04.320 --> 00:16:06.588
But we're gonna get out
of here. I promise. okay?

56
00:16:10.092 --> 00:16:11.526
- My stomach hurts.

57
00:16:13.695 --> 00:16:15.164
- I'll take a look. hm?

58
00:16:15.797 --> 00:16:18.967
Just take a deep
breath and don't move.

59
00:16:19.634 --> 00:16:20.735
