60
00:16:21.669 --> 00:16:22.704
- Emily.

61
00:16:23.139 --> 00:16:24.572
- Lovely name.

62
00:16:24.606 --> 00:16:25.907
I have a baby cousin
with that name.

63
00:16:31.646 --> 00:16:32.781
- It's serious?

64
00:16:34.949 --> 00:16:35.950
- No.

65
00:16:37.353 --> 00:16:38.820
But do something for me.

66
00:16:40.989 --> 00:16:42.258
Just press down here.

67
00:16:42.757 --> 00:16:43.858
And don't look.

68
00:16:44.293 --> 00:16:45.660
I'll be right back. okay?

69
00:16:45.693 --> 00:16:47.595
- No. no. no.

70
00:16:47.629 --> 00:16:48.797
Where are you going?

71
00:16:49.764 --> 00:16:51.267
