to close the wound.

72
00:16:53.302 --> 00:16:54.736
- Am I gonna die?

73
00:16:56.905 --> 00:16:58.340
- Emily. look at me.

74
00:16:59.941 --> 00:17:01.277
I know what I'm doing.

75
00:17:01.310 --> 00:17:02.610
Trust me on this. okay?

76
00:17:03.878 --> 00:17:05.081
Just keep pressing down there.

77
00:17:05.114 --> 00:17:06.282
Everything will be just fine.

78
00:17:06.315 --> 00:17:07.249
I'll be back in a minute.

79
00:17:09.918 --> 00:17:10.952
Okay.

80
00:17:32.308 --> 00:17:33.375
- Alison?

81
00:17:35.211 --> 00:17:36.778
Yes. Emily. I'm here.

82
00:17:36.811 --> 00:17:38.147
Just give me a sec. okay?

83
00:17:42.684 --> 00:17:44.853
- Uh. I think that.

84
00:17:47.356 --> 00:17:48.656
[groans]

85
00:17:50.792 --> 00:17:51.926
- I'm on my way.

86
00:17:55.264 --> 00:17:56.365
Emily?

87
00:17:56.998 --> 00:17:58.167
Are you okay?

88
00:17:59.268 --> 00:18:01.002
