118
00:24:20.516 --> 00:24:22.217
<i>Do you understand this?</i>

119
00:24:22.251 --> 00:24:23.085
<i>I'm worried sick.</i>
<i>I called your father.</i>

120
00:24:23.118 --> 00:24:24.219
