00:51:48.464 --> 00:51:50.266
<i>I'm here with you.</i>

302
00:51:50.299 --> 00:51:51.666
<i>Do you happen to know when</i>
<i>or where you were taken?</i>

303
00:51:52.000 --> 00:51:53.435
